{
  "stem": "9730.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From there, they assigned us to the various units.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it so happened that, in my case, they assigned the team I was with-- we formed teams of six persons-- and the team I was with was assigned to the US 5th Infantry Division, at that time stationed in Northern Ireland.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, I was a Master Sergeant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "32554510.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was attached to the 2nd Infantry Regiment of the 5th Division.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was Colonel [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had an unusual first name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think it was something like [INAUDIBLE] or something like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at that time, I didn't know him too well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I got to know him rather well once, after the, you know, after the invasion and once we got into all the campaigns.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he-- although he was a, a strict disciplinarian, he, he had a, a, a definite human side, too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was-- he seemed interested in, in what had gotten me or, or some of the others, to, to, to that point that we found ourselves in.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And because we were only attached to the division, we actually had our own autonomy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, and, and, they, they-- the regiment could tell us certain things to do, but, but they didn't have jurisdiction over us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that, that was rather nice to enjoy this, this kind of freedom.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But he, he was quite-- I found him to be quite personable.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I guess he thought we must have been of some help to him in determining what units were facing us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was the information I had to get out of interrogation of prisoners of war, which was my assignment.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
